    <div class="ex-body">
      <p>With A − λI = ((3−λ, 1),(1, 3−λ)), calculate the determinant:</p>
      <div class="math-block"><div class="mstep"><div class="mstep-label"></div><div class="mstep-body">det(A − λI) = (3−λ)(3−λ) − 1·1</div></div><div class="mstep"><div class="mstep-label"></div><div class="mstep-body">= (3−λ)² − 1 = 9 − 6λ + λ² − 1</div></div><div class="mstep"><div class="mstep-label"></div><div class="mstep-body">= <strong>λ² − 6λ + 8 = 0</strong></div></div></div>
      <p>Solve with the quadratic formula: λ = (6 ± √(36−32)) / 2 = (6 ± ?) / 2</p>
